sun.jvm.hotspot.debugger.windbg

Class DLL

  • java.lang.Object
    • sun.jvm.hotspot.debugger.windbg.DLL
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LoadObject

    public class DLL
extends java.lang.Object
implements LoadObject
    Provides a simple wrapper around the COFF library which handles relocation. A DLL can represent either a DLL or an EXE file.

      • DLL

        public DLL(Address base)
    throws COFFException
        This constructor was originally used to fetch the DLL's name out of the target process to match it up with the known DLL names, before the fetching of the DLL names and bases was folded into one command. It is no longer used. If it is used, getName() will return null and getSize() will return 0.
        Throws:
        COFFException
